    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[520ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[125ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>milk </strong>– this is your<strong> stock</strong></p>",
