    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the orzo is cooked, add the <strong>spinach</strong> and the <strong>grated cheese</strong> and cook for a further 1-2 min, stirring until wilted</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy mushroom & spinach orzo</strong></p>",
